e adorned with the noblest of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14737,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/24\/sawm-siyam-quran-intercede\/","url_meta":{"origin":17111,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Intercession: Fasting and Quran intercede for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting and the Quran will intercede for the servant on the Day of Resurrection. Fasting will say: O Lord, I prevented him from food and desires during the day, so let me intercede for him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19373,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/20\/honor-nobility-taqwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":17111,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Honor: Nobility is in the fear of Allah, al-Taqwa","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHonor itself is wealth, and nobility is in the fear of Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3271 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647